snippet.textDisplay:
As a proud Sindhi, watching this performance fills my heart with an indescribable sense of pride and joy. Coke Studio has beautifully captured the essence of our culture, from the vibrant colors of Thar to the soulful melodies that resonate with our hearts.
Growing up, I've always cherished our traditions and language, and seeing them showcased on such a platform is truly heartwarming. This performance not only honors our heritage but also serves as a reminder of the rich tapestry of Sindhi culture that we carry with us wherever we go.
Through music, Coke Studio has not only entertained but also educated and enlightened people about the beauty of Sindhi language and traditions. It's moments like these that make me truly grateful to be Sindhi and to belong to such a culturally rich community.

Thank you, Coke Studio, for giving us a platform to celebrate our identity and for promoting unity and diversity through the universal language of music. Jiye Sindh! 🎶

snippet.textDisplay: I am spellbound. The stupendous local ladies singing with such expertise and comfort. Fusion of folk music and rapp, the lyrics based on the folk lore of Marvi returning to her village after successfully defying the lecherous king, the story of women valour in fighting against all the harsh environmental elements,  keeping the culture and traditions alive and most importantly, being the major income providers to the whole family almost singlehandedly. We have to salute the spirit of these beautiful and courageous womenfolks of the most deprived area of Sindh desert. Salutations to the entire team for translating the concept into a vibrant song.
